reviews.review_text: This one sounds the best Nice job.  I don't usually give 5 stars for Auds.  This one is no exception, however, it is a very tight show, and a very good recording.

5 stars I too do not give 5 stars to often. This one has the great sound and balance .  This was a fun tour to be on after being on last 7 or 8 tours consecutively we all really knew each. Is part of what makes a great tour. The fact the Jerry was in a decline health wise did not take away from the music. I think it enhanced it. Blown lyrics happen to every band and every musician. Jerry got down rite spooky sounding on this tour. 
 Thank you Andrew for this tape it captures everything.
